                On Sunday, December 15, Cape Town City Churches also held a Christmas Carols and Picnic in the Park event at the De Waal Park in Oranjezicht. The annual event included live music, carols, picnic, jumping castle, face painting, and festive fun for the whole family. The event was free of charge. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
